---
title: Nonna's Beef Tacos with Caramelised Onion & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: OK, we may be getting a little cheeky with this one, but we know Nonna is all about bringing people around the table to enjoy a meal of wonderful flavours. So when tender herby beef strips, creamy pesto and caramelised onion come together in DIY tacos, we think Nonna would approve.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c074afce3f3394024539144-dba7f64c.jpg
